# Auth Feature Structure Guide

The authentication feature is located in [apps/web/src/features/auth](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth). It contains:

- [login/](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth/login): Login page logic and UI, including [login-form.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth/login/components/login-form.tsx).
- [register/](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth/register): Registration page logic and UI, including [register-form.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth/register/components/register-form.tsx).
- [auth-container.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/features/auth/auth-container.tsx): Shared container for authentication flows.
